
{
    //********ROSALIE DAILY DIALOGUE*************//



    "Introduction": "Hey, have we met? #$b# Sorry, I don't really know everyone...$1 #$b# I'm Rosalie, Gus' niece! I used to live here as a kid and...$1 #$b# ...$2 #$b# Well, enough about me! I'll let you go back to your work!",
           
      "Rosalie.Daily_1": "Can't wait to watch another rerun of the Mortimer Rat Show!$1",
      "Rosalie.Daily_2": "$query !DAY_OF_WEEK Monday#I feel like a cat poster saying they hate Mondays...$3|I feel like a cat poster saying they hate Mondays...$3 #$b# Wait, what do you mean it's not Monday?!$6",
      "Rosalie.Daily_3": "I feel like I was supposed to do something important today...$2 #$b# I feel so dumb... $1",
      "Rosalie.Daily_4": "I feel like I should be in bed by now... #$b# Then I'll be up all night again!$1",
      "Rosalie.Daily_5": "Don't tell Uncle Gus, but my siblings always said I made the best pancakes...$1 #$e# The secret is to cook it in lots of butter... #$e# and chocolate chips, of course!$1 #$e# How much chocolate chips? You measure with your heart, duh!$1",
      "Rosalie.Daily_6": "%Rosalie is humming a catchy theme song from an old sitcom",
      "Rosalie.Daily_7": "%Rosalie seems to be very focused on something right now... It's probably best not to disturb her.",
      "Rosalie.Daily_8": "%Rosalie is staring off into space... Again...",
      "Rosalie.Daily_9": "I wonder what Uncle Gus is cooking up in the kitchen...$0 #$b# I hope it's something good!$1",
      "Rosalie.Daily_10": "Did I forget to take my meds today?...$2 #$b# Ugh, I hate when that happens...$2",
      "Rosalie.Daily_11": "It's days like this I miss the old War Plane Museum...$2 #$b# I wish I had someone to go with...",
      "Rosalie.Daily_12": "I wonder how my sister is doing...$2 #$e# I worry about her sometimes...$2",
      "Rosalie.Daily_13": "%Rosalie appears to be not herself... perhaps it's best to leave her alone",
      "Rosalie.Daily_14": "Can't you see I'm busy?!$5 #$e# I'm sorry, @... I was just... focused on something and... never mind... I'm sorry...$2#$e# %Rosalie is too embarassed to look at you.",
      "Rosalie.Daily_15": "%Rosalie sneezed and now appears to be cradling her left arm. #$e# ...$2",
      "Rosalie.Daily_16": "mmm grilled sans cheese for dinner...$1",
      "Rosalie.Daily_17": "%Rosalie nods to let you know she hears you, but cannot speak back.",

        "Rosalie.Heart2.1": "Is it sad that the person I'm closest to in town is Dr Harvey because I see him the most when I leave the house?$2 #$e# I mean, I don't know if I consider him a friend but he's... my doctor.",
        "Rosalie.Heart2.2": "Uncle Gus has always made the best food! I feel so lucky that he's as good an Uncle as his cooking!$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart2.3": "Hope things are going well for you, @! #$e# Me? Well, it is what it is, you know?$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart2.4": "Sorry if I may seem a bit distant... I'm... not doing well...$2",
    
        "Rosalie.Heart4.1": "I try to drop off coffee for Dr Harvey in the mornings. #$e# It may be the only routine I've kept up with since my diagnosis...es...$2",
        "Rosalie.Heart4.2": "I know that I've been here for a while, but I still don't have it in me to unpack...$2 #$b# I guess a part of me still thinks I'll be leaving soon...$2",
        "Rosalie.Heart4.3": "I'm sorry if I was a bit... cold when we first met...$2 #$b# I've... made it a habit to assume the worse when people want to get to know me...$3 #$e# I still have a hard time remembering 'nice' is different than 'good'.",
        "Rosalie.Heart4.4": "I'm having a surprisinly good day!$1 #$b# Last night, on TV they played a documentary about-$1 #$b# ...$2 #$b# ... never mind. I'll leave you alone forever now...$2",
        "Rosalie.Heart4.5": "Uncle Gus forgot I don't like cheese and put it in my lasagna...$3 #$b# This isn't even a new thing!$3 #$b# I know he's trying his best to feed me and he's housing me and I'm grateful... but it's like... one thing.$2 #$e# Okay, there are others, but cheese is the big one!$5",
        "Rosalie.Heart4.6": "My mom always taught me to see the best in people. #$b# Unfortunately, I have to be cautious of those I let close to me.#$e#Is that why I'm usually so quiet? Trauma works in many ways.$1",

        "Rosalie.Heart6.1": "You know, I never knew Uncle Gus never tried longganisa before. #$b# I know Pierre's and Joja would never sell it here,$2 #$b# but my mom sent me some in the mail, and he loved it!$1 #$e# Maybe he was just glad I was doing the cooking for once, but it's a win in my book!$1 #$e# No, I didn't mean 'lasagna'.$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart6.2": "I watched a video clip last night about how they used to make cartoons back in the 1920s, #$b# Honestly, I have no idea how they had the patience for that, but it's worth it!$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart6.3": "You know, in therapy today, they talked about how boundaries actually start with you. #$b# Like, how can you expect others to follow through and respect them when you don't follow through on what happens when they're broken yourself? #$e# I'm not insinuating anything! I enjoy your company, promise!$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart6.4": "Do you think... Harvey would dance with me instead of Maru if I asked at the flower dance next year?$4 #$b# True, I have to actually make it there to dance...$1 #$e# ... And learn to dance, shut up!$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart6.5": "What exactly is the hype with Joja Cola anyway?$3 #$b# I don't mean to rag on someone's tastes, I know I'm weird too, just... #$b# ...it hurts my tongue...$2",
        "Rosalie.Heart6.6": "%Rosalie is quielty singing an old showtune to herself",
        "Rosalie.Heart6.7": "I used to think that having Harvey be my closest friend in town was a bad thing. #$b# But now, I'm proud to call him one of my best friends. #$e# He actually gets my old references, it's nice...",

        "Rosalie.Heart8.1": "I feel like I can be myself around you, @... #$b# Thank you... for being my friend.$1",
        "Rosalie.Heart8.2": "I just wanted to say... Thank you for being there for me.$1 #$b# It means a lot more than you know.$3",
        "Rosalie.Heart8.3": "You know, I used to have my classmates tell me not to hum in class...$2 #$b# But you... don't seem to mind...",
        "Rosalie.Heart8.4": "I feel so bad for taking over my Uncle Gus' dining room...$2 #$e# I mean, I didn't plan on staying so long but... #$b# Pelican Town... is my home now.$4",


    //NULL4NOW - ROSALIE IS DATING PLAYER// 
